credit.credit-words: Go up with Christ your Head, Your Captain's footsteps see; Follow your Captain, and be led To certain victory. All power to him is given, He ever reigns the same; Salvation, happiness, and heaven Are all in Jesu's name.

Our Captain leads us on; He beckons from the skies, And reaches out a starry crown, And bids us take the prize: Be faithful unto death, Partake My victory; And thou shalt wear this glorious wreath, And thou shalt reign with Me!
